data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. Stunning gated home with private pool located in the popular Mallory Park.  Designer touches throughout. Enjoy family movies in your media/game room or dinner on your designer outdoor oasis. High end Sonos surround sound speakers add life to the first floor and backyard lanai.  Oversized sliding door opens up to extend your living area into the mosquito free enclosed backyard. Lots of natural light. Tankless water heater, epoxy garage floor, and custom Master closet with built-ins. Multiple sitting areas. This home was designed to entertain and impress! Walking distance to highly rated Elementary and Middle School. Beautiful tropical trails with zipline park, fishing ponds, fitness center, spa, dog park, fire pit, grill, tennis and basketball courts. You will love this resort style living. You won’t want to miss this one! There is an option to purchase fully furnished.
